KitKat::
She nodded to Koj as he bowed to her. She had never had a bot bow to 
her. She smiled at him. "I am pleased to meet you. What is your name?"

She blushed as he gave her the flower. She smiled and inhaled the 
fragrence of hte flower. It had a sweet scent.  She smiled at them.
"I...ah..well..Thank you for the beautiful flower, but why are you 
here?"


DarkMouse::
She leaned over and whispered to GoldenEye,"I don't trust these two."

GoldenEye::
Whispers back," I'm with you. I don't like this. But then again, it's 
up to  KitKat."

DarkMouse::
She nodded. "Yeah. Just keep your eagle eyes peeled."
